{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"m75y7l3tusc1xrp3atjv1jz","title":"Webpack","desc":"","updated":1687535034623,"created":1687534628804,"custom":{},"fname":"web-components.extra-tools.webpack","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"0365645532c2ae830a58f683e489ee28","links":[{"from":{"fname":"web-components.deployment.browser-support","id":"l1ofcgjdkle0j55lk21ujrq","vaultName":"docs"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":58,"column":1,"offset":3556},"end":{"line":58,"column":40,"offset":3595},"indent":[]},"value":"web-components.extra-tools.webpack"}],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"axqprxc8srd9y6d7vh3kc7l","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"webpack\">Webpack<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#webpack\"></a></h1>\n<p>Webpack es un empaquetador de modulos y dpeendencias para aplicaciones web. Facilita el tomar todas las dependencias de nuestro proyecto y enpaquetarlas en un solo archivo facil de distribuir en un ambiente productivo.\nWebpack puede empaquetar distintos tipos de assets por medio de plugins. Pro ejemplo si queremos usar un preprocesador de CSS como Less o Sass, podríamos usar un plugin de webpack para observar estos archivos y compilarlos. En este caso usaremos Babel para compilar y empaquetar nuestro codigo ES2015 a ES5.</p>\n<p>Primero creamos el webpack.config.js</p>\n<pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> path <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'path'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">exports</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">entry</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./src/index.js'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">output</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">path</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> path<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">resolve</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>__dirname<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'dist'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">filename</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'index.js'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">library</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'webComponent'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">libraryTarget</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'umd'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Esta es la configuración mínima de Webpack. El <code>entry</code> es el main de nuestra librería. Desde ese archivo Webpack empezará y resolverá cualquier dependencia (imporst). El <code>output</code> define donde se va a generar el codigo compilado. También define su nombre y que tipo de archivo JavaScript va a ser.</p>\n<p>Ahora podemos correr el comando</p>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> run build\n</code></pre>\n<p>Si vamos a la carpeta dist vamos a ver un <code>index.js</code> compilado a ES5 que será compatible con IE11.</p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/l1ofcgjdkle0j55lk21ujrq\">Browser Support</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"guomymvu5xxkrbvedoncjdw","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1687553787663,"created":1687478467553,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb6d2289d9babdad43709e4ff265bef2","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"guomymvu5xxkrbvedoncjdw","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"https://webcomponent.dev/","alias":"Cory Rylan","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":94,"offset":117},"end":{"line":4,"column":134,"offset":157},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"https://webcomponent.dev/"}}],"anchors":{"web-components-docs":{"type":"header","text":"Web Components DOCS","value":"web-components-docs","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1}},"children":["zkfccjgcs7b7pqvirwby57p"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\n# Web Components DOCS\n\nEsta es una documentación de web components basada en el libro *Web Component Essentials* de [[Cory Rylan|https://webcomponent.dev/]]\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true,"enableSelfContainedVaults":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"vaults":[{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"task","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"asOwnDo